            "failure_message": "Wistful disappointment: disappointment + sadness with low arousal, negative valence, and not in rage/despair/grief collapse. Adds affiliation-drop / affiliation-crossing as an extra ‘missed connection’ pathway even when bonding emotions are gated low by disengagement."
